{"snp2.13:0.1":"Sutta Nipata 2.13 ","snp2.13:0.2":"Sammaparibbajaniyasutta ","snp2.13:1.1":"“Pucchami munim pahutapannam, ","snp2.13:1.2":"Tinnam parangatam parinibbutam thitattam; ","snp2.13:1.3":"Nikkhamma ghara panujja kame, ","snp2.13:1.4":"Katham bhikkhu samma so loke paribbajeyya”. ","snp2.13:2.1":"“Yassa mangala samuhata, ","snp2.13:2.2":"(iti bhagava) ","snp2.13:2.3":"Uppata supina ca lakkhana ca; ","snp2.13:2.4":"So mangaladosavippahino, ","snp2.13:2.5":"Samma so loke paribbajeyya. ","snp2.13:3.1":"Ragam vinayetha manusesu, ","snp2.13:3.2":"Dibbesu kamesu capi bhikkhu; ","snp2.13:3.3":"Atikkamma bhavam samecca dhammam, ","snp2.13:3.4":"Samma so loke paribbajeyya. ","snp2.13:4.1":"Vipitthikatvana pesunani, ","snp2.13:4.2":"Kodham kadariyam jaheyya bhikkhu; ","snp2.13:4.3":"Anurodhavirodhavippahino, ","snp2.13:4.4":"Samma so loke paribbajeyya. ","snp2.13:5.1":"Hitvana piyanca appiyanca, ","snp2.13:5.2":"Anupadaya anissito kuhinci; ","snp2.13:5.3":"Samyojaniyehi vippamutto, ","snp2.13:5.4":"Samma so loke paribbajeyya. ","snp2.13:6.1":"Na so upadhisu sarameti, ","snp2.13:6.2":"Adanesu vineyya chandaragam; ","snp2.13:6.3":"So anissito anannaneyyo, ","snp2.13:6.4":"Samma so loke paribbajeyya. ","snp2.13:7.1":"Vacasa manasa ca kammuna ca, ","snp2.13:7.2":"Aviruddho samma viditva dhammam; ","snp2.13:7.3":"Nibbanapadabhipatthayano, ","snp2.13:7.4":"Samma so loke paribbajeyya. ","snp2.13:8.1":"Yo vandati manti nunnameyya, ","snp2.13:8.2":"Akkutthopi na sandhiyetha bhikkhu; ","snp2.13:8.3":"Laddha parabhojanam na majje, ","snp2.13:8.4":"Samma so loke paribbajeyya. ","snp2.13:9.1":"Lobhanca bhavanca vippahaya, ","snp2.13:9.2":"Virato chedanabandhana ca bhikkhu; ","snp2.13:9.3":"So tinnakathankatho visallo, ","snp2.13:9.4":"Samma so loke paribbajeyya. ","snp2.13:10.1":"Saruppam attano viditva, ","snp2.13:10.2":"No ca bhikkhu himseyya kanci loke; ","snp2.13:10.3":"Yathatathiyam viditva dhammam, ","snp2.13:10.4":"Samma so loke paribbajeyya. ","snp2.13:11.1":"Yassanusaya na santi keci, ","snp2.13:11.2":"Mula ca akusala samuhatase; ","snp2.13:11.3":"So niraso anasisano, ","snp2.13:11.4":"Samma so loke paribbajeyya. ","snp2.13:12.1":"Asavakhino pahinamano, ","snp2.13:12.2":"Sabbam ragapatham upativatto; ","snp2.13:12.3":"Danto parinibbuto thitatto, ","snp2.13:12.4":"Samma so loke paribbajeyya. ","snp2.13:13.1":"Saddho sutava niyamadassi, ","snp2.13:13.2":"Vaggagatesu na vaggasari dhiro; ","snp2.13:13.3":"Lobham dosam vineyya patigham, ","snp2.13:13.4":"Samma so loke paribbajeyya. ","snp2.13:14.1":"Samsuddhajino vivattacchado, ","snp2.13:14.2":"Dhammesu vasi paragu anejo; ","snp2.13:14.3":"Sankharanirodhananakusalo, ","snp2.13:14.4":"Samma so loke paribbajeyya. ","snp2.13:15.1":"Atitesu anagatesu capi, ","snp2.13:15.2":"Kappatito aticcasuddhipanno; ","snp2.13:15.3":"Sabbayatanehi vippamutto, ","snp2.13:15.4":"Samma so loke paribbajeyya. ","snp2.13:16.1":"Annaya padam samecca dhammam, ","snp2.13:16.2":"Vivatam disvana pahanamasavanam; ","snp2.13:16.3":"Sabbupadhinam parikkhayano, ","snp2.13:16.4":"Samma so loke paribbajeyya”. ","snp2.13:17.1":"“Addha hi bhagava tatheva etam, ","snp2.13:17.2":"Yo so evamvihari danto bhikkhu; ","snp2.13:17.3":"Sabbasamyojanayogavitivatto, ","snp2.13:17.4":"Samma so loke paribbajeyya”ti. ","snp2.13:17.5":"Sammaparibbajaniyasuttam terasamam. "}